    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior are clean, you will find some minor signs of normal wear, such as small stone chips on the hood and slight creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, it is a dependable, attractive car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
