    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a brand new home for my trusty ride. It has been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape, just waiting for its next big adventure! I\u2019ve truly loved driving this car and have kept it well-maintained so it\u2019s ready to hit the road whenever you are. It\u2019s a solid, smooth drive that I know you're going to love. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'm super happy to chat and help you out!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
