      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the 3.6L M96 horizontally opposed six-cylinder, delivering 320 hp through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical highlights include a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal. The chassis retains its factory poise with a multi-link rear suspension and four-piston monobloc calipers clamping cross-drilled rotors. While showing minor signs of spirited road use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders and the Bosch Motronic engine management ensures a stable idle and linear throttle response. A turn-key driver for the purist seeking an analog connection to the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Runs well.",
