    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between performance and comfort. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a careful eye will spot a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014standard signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The leather seating is plush and intact, showing only light softening on the driver's bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly; it has a documented service history with a recent fluid flush and brake pad replacement. While there is some very light wear on the steering wheel texture, the overall interior feels fresh and inviting. This car drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers a reliable, high-quality experience for its next owner. I have priced this fairly to ensure a transparent and straightforward transaction.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
